    <div class="section">
      <h3>HISTORY OF PRESENT ILLNESS</h3>
      <h4>1ST COMPLAINT: CONFUSION</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Onset: When did the confusion start?
          <ul>
            <li>Sudden</li>
            <ul>
              can have a renal cause but have to rule out other causes
              <li>After a head injury</li>
              <li>After a stroke</li>
              <li>After a seizure</li>
              <li>etc...</li>
            </ul>
            <li>Gradual</li>
            <ul>
              can have a renal cause but have to rule out other causes
              <li>After a head injury</li>
              <li>Dementia</li>
              <li>etc...</li>
            </ul>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Duration: How long has the confusion been present?</li>
        <li>Progression: Has the confusion been getting worse?</li>
        <li>Associated Symptoms:
          <ul>
            <li>Decreased urine output</li>
            <li>Swelling of legs</li>
            <li>Shortness of breath</li>
            <li>Nausea/vomiting</li>
            <li>Weakness</li>
            <li>Seizures</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Triggers: Any known triggers or precipitating factors?</li>
        <li>Prior episodes: Has this happened before?</li>
        <li>Medications: Any recent changes in medications?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
